author: LeadSeason (leadseason)
install:
Various planetside related slash commands.
To set service id use '[p]setserviceid <You service id>'. You can get your own from https://census.daybreakgames.com/#devSignup 
Make sure to enable slash commands with '[p]slash enablecog planetside'
name: CogNado
end_user_data_statement: This cog only currently stores Census serviceID. This might change in the future.
